Privacy Policy
Prune uses the game engine, Unity. See their privacy policy here:
Unity Privacy Policy
As of version 1.1.3 Prune does not collect any data whatsoever. Prior to that version Prune collected basic data like device type and play time for crash and analytics purposes.
If you have any questions about the privacy policy please contact
support@prunegame.com
.
